modelCheckCTL.model
Class LabelCTLAlg

java.lang.Object
  modelCheckCTL.model.LabelCTLAlg

public class LabelCTLAlg
extends java.lang.Object

This object brings together the kripke structure the formula and the starting state to determine if a current formula holds or if it fails for a given model.
